                            11B Eltharwa Almaadanya st.<br>
                            1 Gate (KHOFO)- Hadayek Al-Ahram-Giza-Egypt.<br>
                            <a href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-earphone ">@Resources.Main.Email</span>: info@iatlcegypt.com</a><br>
                            <a href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-earphone ">@Resources.Main.Phone</span>: +2 0233801999</a><br>
